This is very effective for:
- **Saving Tokens**: AI only receives relevant clean data.
- **Speed**: Extraction operations are performed locally by Scrapling.
- **Accuracy**: Ensures AI gets the latest data from the web in real-time.

### Quick Installation

You can start trying <span class="highlight">Scrapling</span> with just one command:

```bash
pip install scrapling
# For full features with browser engine
pip install "scrapling[fetchers]"
scrapling install
```

## Conclusion

The presence of <span class="highlight">Scrapling</span> marks the end of the fragile and easily detectable scraping era. For anyone serious about data or artificial intelligence development, this tool is a mandatory addition to your tech stack.

